酸但派體是好吃的，不管平日假日人潮很多一定要訂位，不然就要現場等候一會了\",\"time\":1745160612,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"YY H (Julia)\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114304184712731902219/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMqTESaAbGqnFl1B-YGj5MRumPie9SklJDjacJ7iLkcAeLniiH=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 個月前\",\"text\":\"😋餐點好吃！\\n🤓服務很好！\\n🥳用餐氣氛佳！\\n🤩MENU也用心製作～\\n\\n只是佐料🧂例如：鹽和糖包～建議可以主動詢問或提供，因為沒有任何服務人員一直盯場，你想要任何東西就要等其中一位服務人員🙎跟我有眼神👀對焦，才能呼喚後拿到。\\n\\n其他都非常棒！\",\"time\":1739868737,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"YuRu Chen\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115298789530008518559/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWvh1pyVzm0RcRKBzWjnK2cl4hFRvQNE8Lb4sf6GgmfiVpGq2lFAw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 個月前\",\"text\":\"甜點很好吃！熱水果茶可以加熱水回沖，甜點不太會踩雷的店，有供應鹹食下次吃看看。\\n一如既往人很多，平日（禮拜三）13:30左右非用餐時間來的，一樣滿位要等候電話通知，真的是新竹日常，在新竹不只我跟朋友不用上班，似乎不用上班的人好多啊😂😂幸福城市。\\n不過不會等太久就排到了，餐點可掃描點餐，上餐速度很快，離開前再拿收據報櫃檯結帳即可。\",\"time\":1741485014,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNS0WU8Bs7CkCvp9PeeC0j3jfr8rTT_FYmTu_UlYAqSTs_zmfL6oEXSN_iuMOVmMW5_mrCseUmhMSJADFuaYAgucMvcyCgvYhWr17uP3evvbxgLjIAKrM7D7rIdn0rIaf3SaWf3xEfhBYfwcsFVb4mcVsYOpr0SjPxEOaTrNLKzumTj1ogvWRjX7XmXryGH9BfWqCm3tYMxQCkbuzYb4Y6Itvzr664iVW_sYv8ZEVZ-HQ-SHBkffFI_dPlj3VzDQonAjkeJ8xkwIkl2n6RpzAUrAkN41O1J1wr8hepQmYRzamP0C5s4McCzrYdD_9hgxNzNuCXLfkx0\",\"AXQCQNTmtg1tuRvp5mMnGtXQpAAc_UAKEMzoWrIssj7DN1tsWVLntPb6HmBB1LZwaROfjvronUxHxggpEOfCPEFZhxmim7MLf5ZlRbJJ-heqgUIjvkQOaub6Swbg7B2NEa5hbHO-685jRfWlJqvxxG9gdAVihqz24E8SnyQZAIR-AxsgbmujFqW15721fhS2PD47z-fwLzS_qZImbVrdcDCwsG5muvyEFMgckpN3ZTXAVoyMTFf53ZruEvL9BlKrcczBK--e03-cDWv7RpUfHzSoeKVlf6GTzbOrauefYWOa1-jv3ThP-O519-YGjmjYxKSckmMFYGrNQMLsqoqwDqvCNaNYIk-jfWyyfTChmgvlFYoBdYZZbhC7qi-x-maTYrRPLpoQpvQ4rkxk9Hb-bc4epcSqfhAj70ib4ISX_cvhK7cdr18p2RkK9MpfglWRPtZzuM55